@startuml
' Diagram: F10 - Dashboard tong quan va monitoring CMS (Sequence)
' Status: VERIFIED
' Baseline: branch master, current worktree @ HEAD 0121e4f
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/Index.cshtml.cs: OnGetAsync(), ResolveRange(), LoadPoiSectionAsync(), LoadAnalyticsWithRetryAsync(), LoadAnalyticsAsync(), LoadActivityAsync(), LoadGeoAsync(), LoadTopPoiAsync(), LoadRevenueAsync(), LoadSummaryAsync(), FillMissingBuckets()
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/Index.cshtml
' Note: Sequence chi tiet hoa ResolveRange(), 2 pha load POI/analytics, shared connection, va serialize JSON cho chart/heatmap/revenue.
' Note: Sequence chi the hien method/step cua IndexModel va persistence helper, khong liet ke cau SQL.
' Note: 3 the thong ke o stats-grid: TongPOI (tat ca POI ke ca chua gia han), POIDangHoatDong (TrangThai=true va con han duy tri), Ngon ngu (3).
title F10 - Dashboard tong quan va monitoring CMS

actor Admin
control "CMS IndexModel" as IndexModel
participant "AppDbContext\n<<persistence>>" as DbContext
participant "Analytics read helper" as AnalyticsRead
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Admin -> IndexModel: OnGetAsync(mode, date, week, month, year, from, to)
IndexModel -> IndexModel: ResolveRange()
note right of IndexModel
  Mode:
  today, yesterday, last7, last30,
  thismonth, lastmonth, last12m,
  day, week, month, year, custom
end note

IndexModel -> DbContext: LoadPoiSectionAsync()
DbContext -> DB: read POI and MonAn rows
DB --> DbContext: POIs
DbContext --> IndexModel: POIs
note right of IndexModel
  LoadPoiSectionAsync() computes:
  TongPOI, POIDangHoatDong,
  and SoQuanQuaHan.
end note

IndexModel -> IndexModel: LoadAnalyticsWithRetryAsync()
IndexModel -> DbContext: Database.GetDbConnection()
DbContext --> IndexModel: connection
IndexModel -> AnalyticsRead: LoadActivityAsync(conn, since, until, granularity)
AnalyticsRead -> DB: read activity buckets
DB --> AnalyticsRead: ActivityBuckets
AnalyticsRead --> IndexModel: ActivityBuckets

IndexModel -> AnalyticsRead: LoadGeoAsync(conn, since, until)
AnalyticsRead -> DB: read geo points
DB --> AnalyticsRead: GeoPoints
AnalyticsRead --> IndexModel: GeoPoints

IndexModel -> AnalyticsRead: LoadTopPoiAsync(conn, since, until)
AnalyticsRead -> DB: read top POI metrics
DB --> AnalyticsRead: TopPoi
AnalyticsRead --> IndexModel: TopPoi

IndexModel -> AnalyticsRead: LoadRevenueAsync(conn, since, until, granularity)
AnalyticsRead -> DB: read revenue buckets
DB --> AnalyticsRead: RevenueBuckets
AnalyticsRead --> IndexModel: RevenueBuckets

IndexModel -> AnalyticsRead: LoadSummaryAsync(conn, since, until)
AnalyticsRead -> DB: read summary metrics
DB --> AnalyticsRead: summary
AnalyticsRead --> IndexModel: summary

IndexModel -> IndexModel: FillMissingBuckets()\nSerialize ActivityJson/GeoJson/RevenueJson
IndexModel --> Admin: render dashboard + monitoring section
@enduml
